components.description: Downloads JMA weather station CSV data from the HTTPS endpoint and provides it via XCom.

components.description: Downloads MetOffice weather station CSV data from the HTTPS endpoint and provides it via XCom.

components.name: Download BOM Data
components.description: Downloads BOM weather station CSV data from the HTTPS endpoint and provides it via XCom.

components.name: Normalize NOAA Data
components.description: Normalizes NOAA CSV data to a standard format (ISO timestamp, Celsius temperature, meters elevation).
